            <a class="favouritable" data-favourite-url="/favourites/add?resource_id=87&amp;resource_type=Person" data-tooltip="Maksim Zakhartsev" href="/people/87"><img alt="" src="/assets/avatar-images/376-60x60.png" /></a>
